metadata.name: Bellone, Goddess of war.
metadata.description:
NEW ANCESTRAL #1 //

This piece is inspired by Athena.

I wanted to reinvent the goddess represented in the past through a futuristic society based on exosquellettes.

I loved contrasting the gentleness of women with the violence of the equipment they have. 

DEGITAL + PHYSICAL DELIVERING:

- Bellone, Goddess of war digital artwork

- High quality 70x 87,2 cm print on acrylic glass
